high_descs: Turn to the right, then the left to find the microwave.
Pick up the knife from the center of the counter in front of you.
Take the knife and turn to around, then left to locate the stove.
Place the knife in the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan from the front left burner of the stove.
Carry the pan and turn to the left, and move to the counter.
Place the pan and knife on the back side of the counter, behind the loaf of bread and to the left.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and knife to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter above the dishwasher on the left.
Pick up the knife to the right of the spatula.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the left.
Place the knife inside the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn left and walk to the counter straight ahead with the loaf of bread.
Place the pan down on the counter behind the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: To move a pan with a knife to the counter with the bread.

high_descs: Turn right walk forward then turn left on the counter above the washer
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right walk forward turn left to the stove
Put the knife in the pan
Pick up the pan with knife from the stove
Turn left walk forward to the counter
Put the pan with knife on the high level of the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with knife on the counter
